share/70777388caf7c1ad7f5c3e9577f88a77","link_m3u8":"https://vip.opstream15.com/20241225/46128_70777388/index.m3u8"}]}],"time":"44 phút/tập","description":"The Szema family murdered the Tong family in order to monopolize the weapons industry. Twenty years later, the chief of Brocade Guards, YUEMAN FUNG (CHENG SIU CHOW, ADAM), fights against MRS. WONG (WANG MING CHUN, LIZA) of the biggest escort carrier in town. During the fight, they realize they might know each other… FUNG has changed his name, put on an eye patch and become a Brocade Guard. His wife, TONG PIK, has married WONG. They live with humiliation while they wait for the day of revenge. However, they both are in situations where they can’t reveal their identities. PIK hires MANG LUI (LAM RAYMOND) as a fighter. He falls in love with PIK’s daughter YEE (YEUNG SZE KI, SHIRLEY). Ironically, LUI is PIK’s son, whom she lost many years ago, and so love between the two is impossible. How can love and hatred end between two generations?","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"109215","season":1,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},"modified":"2024-12-25T20:19:14.000Z","cast":["Trịnh Thiếu Thu","Liza Wong Ming-Chuen","Lâm Phong","Dương Tư Kỳ","Yang Xue","Chen Hung-Lieh","Lư Hải Bằng","Lý Gia Đỉnh","Shen Baoping","Vương Đức Thuận","Tsui Wing","Hà Khải Nam","Kong Hon","Gregory Lee Wing-Hor","Vu Dương"],"director":["Thích Kỳ Nghĩa"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Trịnh Thiếu Thu","name_vi":"Trịnh Thiếu Thu","name_original":"Adam Cheng Siu-Chow","tmdb_id":82401,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/KHy7b3kAXP05VGcdsPy3Qf34GM.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/82401"},{"name":"Liza Wong Ming-Chuen","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Liza Wong Ming-Chuen","tmdb_id":240159,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oElwuzlAtF5VobV0ElRt0ZvW5gN.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/240159"},{"name":"Lâm Phong","name_vi":"Lâm Phong","name_original":"Raymond Lam Fung","tmdb_id":89409,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w